    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox delivering power to the rear wheels via a Variable M Differential Lock. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension. Technical highlights include a recent VANOS system overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly is within spec. The atmospheric induction note is crisp, and the hydraulic steering rack provides the precise feedback expected of this iconic platform.",
