      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for enthusiast car. The exterior retains its original factory luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular road use. All body panels are straight with consistent gaps, and the alloy wheels are free of major curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free environment; the premium leather upholstery is supple, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster and no tears. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has followed a strict maintenance schedule with synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. Most recently, the brake pads and rotors were replaced, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. The engine pulls smoothly through the rev range, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner, offering a perfect balance of reliability and performance.",
